{"tid":1512473,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"山神勢外借國米 唔走聽踢盃仔","createTime":"2019-08-28T01:54:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-28T02:26:34.000Z","uid":153600,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"3701f4304957fda0d4cc013845746511ca40f3ef","tid":1512473,"uid":153600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T01:54:18.000Z","msg":"【Now Sports-體育】BBC指，曼聯球星阿歷斯山齊士已拍板外借至國際米蘭，與前隊友盧卡古再度合作。<br />\n<br />\nBBC指，曼聯棄將阿歷斯山齊士（Alexis Sanchez）周二已飛赴米蘭，完成外借國際米蘭的轉會。國際米蘭同意支付山齊士的450萬英鎊，但據悉沒有打算正式把他羅致旗下。這名智利球星周三將進行體測，屆時將正式與前曼聯隊友盧卡古合作。<br />\n<br />\n曼聯早已想把高薪的山齊士趕走，於是明確告知山齊士，他將不會獲得重用，有指若山神留隊，只會在歐霸盃和英聯盃的賽事中上陣。山齊士在曼聯周薪高達40萬英鎊，可惜2018年1月加盟以來，僅僅取得4個入波，表現與薪水相去太遠。<br />\n<br />\n30歲的山齊士遭遇職業生涯最大低潮，主要原因在他自己身上，2018年1月他拒絕加盟曼城，卻選擇了内部不穩的曼聯。<br />\n<br />\n如果當初去曼城，應該一早捧咗英超<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83edf1cd3b7f3c839e948041a863b5c24aac4130","tid":1512473,"uid":89145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T01:54:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1d8e874c29f18a739e3939078521fcb30508c953","tid":1512473,"uid":284522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T01:55:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PWzcvgg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPWzcvgg.jpg&h=187c67d0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n九月一號下午一點機場見<br />\n<br />\n901機場和你塞 Channel<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=zAhFImnUcMh%2FonyB55KWQ4bCTaNrw2SAqZBfI0xY0Mo%3D&h=a08a9e60\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyou</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 公海<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyouopen&d=zAhFImnUcMh%2FonyB55KWQ4bCTaNrw2SAqZBfI0xY0Mo%3D&h=c98acbcc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyouopen</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 宣傳<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyoupromote\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.